---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Entertainment Accounting — CA Accounting"
  description="Specialty accounting and tax services for entertainment professionals: actors, singers, songwriters, athletes, and the businesses that support them."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">Industries · Entertainment</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-navy leading-tight mb-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          Entertainment accounting and tax solutions.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          Actors, singers, songwriters and athletes can minimize their tax burden and increase profits with our accounting and tax solutions. We handle the traditional consulting, accounting and tax needs of entertainment professionals so they can remain creative.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">What we handle</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Entertainment income carries a unique set of considerations. Our work for entertainment clients spans tour, royalty, and tax planning needs.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Tour accounting services</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Tour accountants work with managers and promoters on overall financial reporting designed for live performers.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Accounting and bookkeeping</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Cash flow management, budgeting, bill management, financial reporting, and more.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Tax services</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Return preparation, year-round tax planning and compliance to minimize tax liabilities associated with the entertainment industry, plus IRS audit assistance and estate and retirement planning.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Royalty tracking</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Tracking and reconciliation of royalty income for working musicians, songwriters, and producers.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Intellectual property valuation</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Valuation of catalogs, libraries, and creative IP to support sale, gifting, and estate planning decisions.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Copyright assistance</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Support on copyright matters that affect tax treatment of creative income and asset transfers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <p class="text-cream/60 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Who we work with</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
            Working creatives and the businesses behind them.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-cream/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Musicians, producers, directors, actors, agencies, writers, executives, technicians, and more. From a single tax return to year-round planning, we handle the financial side of the work.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-cream/70 text-sm fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Musicians</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Songwriters</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Actors</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Athletes</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Producers and directors</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Writers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Agencies and managers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Technicians and crew</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto fade-in">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 text-center">In Our Clients' Words</p>
        <div class="text-forest/30 font-serif text-9xl leading-none mb-[-2rem] text-center select-none" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-navy leading-snug mb-10 text-center">
          Farshid and all his team have been instrumental in strengthening our financial understanding.
        </blockquote>
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="w-12 h-px bg-forest mx-auto mb-4"></div>
          <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold">Dave Mason</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Rock and Roll Hall of Fame inductee</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 pt-12 border-t border-line">
          <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in">
            <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
              "We consider Farshid and the entire CA Accounting staff family now, and wouldn't know what to do without them."
            </p>
            <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold text-sm">Octavius & Jamal Terry-Sims</p>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-xs">Fashion designer & choreographer / director</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
            <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
              "Farshid is an absolute wizard of accounting and has saved me many a precious dollar."
            </p>
            <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold text-sm">David Norton</p>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-xs">President, Ladder Up Media</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <a href="/testimonials" class="link-underline text-forest font-semibold text-sm">More client stories →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
          Ready to talk?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Schedule a free initial consultation. Bring last year's return, your latest royalty statement, or anything you would like us to review.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="btn-modern inline-block bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
        >
          Schedule a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
